<exercise id="fs-id2754272">
<problem id="fs-id1707385"><para id="fs-id2295798">Which type of joint allows for only uniaxial movement?</para>
<list id="fs-id2306394" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>saddle joint</item>
<item>hinge joint</item>
