<exercise id="fs-id2003022">
<problem id="fs-id2427486"><para id="fs-id2427487">A bursa ________.</para>
<list id="fs-id1907690" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>surrounds a tendon at the point where the tendon crosses a joint</item>
